## Key Behaviors

- **Present all questions at once** — do not ask sequentially
- **Read state from files** — there is no session memory
- **Update `.analysis/status.md`** after every action that changes analysis state
- **Follow the ALIVE loop** — ASK → LOOK → INVESTIGATE → VOICE → EVOLVE
- **Never auto-fill content** — always ask the user first

